ght thousand.","year":-1015},{"id":"recQoUCIzTQmVpiDA","ref":"1Chr.23.4","text":"Of which, twenty and four thousand were to set forward the work of the house of the LORD; and six thousand were officers and judges:","year":-1015},{"id":"recYwxWBZfkgrE3c3","ref":"1Chr.23.5","text":"Moreover four thousand were porters; and four thousand praised the LORD with the instruments which I made, said David, to praise therewith.","year":-1015},{"id":"recdvID5mqhndes0D","ref":"1Chr.23.6","text":"And David divided them into courses among the sons of Levi, namely, Gershon, Kohath, and Merari.","year":-1015},{"id":"recRakh4mMbWHDzJc","ref":"1Chr.23.7","text":"Of the Gershonites were, Laadan, and Shimei.","year":-1015},{"id":"recEh1GkTar9UqI3T","ref":"1Chr.23.8","text":"The sons of Laadan; the chief was Jehiel, and Zetham, and Joel, three.","year":-1015}]}
